    _
  1. A greater number of expressions._
  2. A greater number of non-negated expressions with a concrete value._
_

It is assumed that both instances have been obtained via_{@link #getMatchingCondition(HttpServletRequest)} and each instance_contains the matching parameter expressions only or is otherwise empty.
